simple diagram.png
framework1.png

# Raw and derived data
*.pq
*.parquet
*.feather
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.npy
*.npz
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
eq_data_stage*/
eq_resp_stage*/
